data.description: Discover the best of small-town living paired with community in this welcoming neighborhood! Step into this light-filled 5-bed, 3-bath home, built in 2012, on nearly 1/4 acre. The heart of the home features an open-concept layout connecting the kitchen, dining, and living areas all leading to the back deck and spacious yard — perfect for your gatherings of all sizes! Also upstairs, the primary bedroom awaits with en suite bathroom, along with two more bedrooms and another full bath, providing ample space for everyone. Downstairs features the laundry room, a third bathroom, and two additional bedrooms – with the fifth bedroom as yours to define, whether it's a home office, a den, or whatever your heart desires. The garage isn't just for parking; it features a wood stove to keep you toasty while tackling projects. This ideal location is only a stone's throw from the neighborhood park and a short stroll from the Deer Park Golf Course. Ask us about a 1st year lender paid interest rate buydown!
